oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Cabinet with Wood Type
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Hatch Show Print (Firm);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Color photo of a cabinet, in the Hatch Show Print shop on 4th Avenue, filled with wood type. Some of the cabinet's drawers are open to display the type. A handwritten note on the back of the photo says, "116 4th Ave. S," which is a reference to the shop's location where the photo was taken.
